{"tid":203861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"村屋謀殺案：75歲租客講足兩日大話終被捕","createTime":"2017-04-16T15:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T17:09:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5899c07e260f36d185ba49b2204311849b0a798b","tid":203861,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170416/photo/bkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170416230652\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170416%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170416230652&h=af682e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n疑兇(圓圈)早上返現場助查，晚上被捕。（文健雄/冼耀華攝）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170416/photo/bkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001_02b.jpg?20170416230652\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170416%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20170416230652&h=1b92d2e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【21:00】探員在現場調查後，帶走一袋證物檢驗。<br />\n<br />\n【19:00】消息指，案發單位一名75歲姓倪男住客，因接受警方查問時口供有破綻，警方覺得有可疑，調查後懷疑他與案有關，將其拘捕。有人聲稱因不忿包租公「講壞話」，激動下用硬物襲擊其頭部致死。疑犯晚上被警方押回現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n元朗田廈路田心村一名包租公遭殺害兇案，新界北總區重案組10多名探員，通宵留守現場蒐證，至今日清晨6時許仍未結束；由於案中死者經法醫初步檢驗，頭部有多處遭重擊痕迹，故相信事主曾遭人用硬物連番施襲，惟警方經過通宵大規模搜索，至今未尋獲兇器。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，探員在現場調查期間，封鎖田心村村口，對出入該村人士進行查問，如證實為該村村民或村內居住人士，始讓其返回住所。<br />\n<br />\n兇案於昨晨10時許揭發，一名人稱「平叔」的村民，因近日不見影蹤，且房間傳出惡臭，被鄰居揭發倒斃房內。警方到場發現他身體發脹，屍水四濺，懷疑曾被人由床上搬落地面，加上他頭部遭被單蓋住，天靈蓋及頭部有多處被重擊痕迹，且手機及個人財物不翼而飛，遂將案件改列謀殺，交由新界北總區重案組跟進。經法醫檢驗，相信死者已死去2至3日。<br />\n<br />\n初步相信死者為李平（66歲），人稱「平叔」。據悉，平叔育有一子一女，閒時會在村內與街坊賭錢。現場為田心村1幢3層高村屋，地下被間成3間房間，平叔為包租公，住在其中1間房間，其餘2間房分租予2名中年漢。昨晨10時許，有街坊發現已數日不見平叔，且房間傳出惡臭，遂從窗戶查看，赫見他倒臥房間內了無反應，遂慌忙報警。警員接報到場，消防協助破門而入，發現事主倒卧房內，已無氣息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170416/bkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170416%2Fbkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001.html&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=e2ccc305\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170416/bkn-20170416054621550-0416_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ef4f4757942610ab5571fbeaf0e35293e505bef9","tid":203861,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"勇武廢老vs有錢廢老"},{"pid":"692a53a29676e93b54db61aac294d0b80e4b1eeb","tid":203861,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8afd8edfa58592fd2587dce001af1b0ec468c9","tid":203861,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:57:04.000Z","msg":"敬下老好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a34ffd8651fa275b1d312d5e62ba59e5c9f72a4","tid":203861,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"廢老殺廢老"},{"pid":"715f021a819f5b0525de00a2ad3646b892f6b106","tid":203861,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:00:23.000Z","msg":"咁即係講左咩大話,俾差佬揭穿?"},{"pid":"0274f2e40535f8e66ac2a9d9c29382d4e5f7fc9d","tid":203861,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:01:12.000Z","msg":"廢老"},{"pid":"5e6b932c7bef5b3eda3d399bf0eb75a1432f9b87","tid":203861,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:03:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d5759de95baf0295ce844fb1235d8f2a1d482ab","tid":203861,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"警車有無關愛座"},{"pid":"392d5469cbad4282c0206b0ead873bd426c30ca9","tid":203861,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"死係監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bb6e97b6aeef0b245555b1528cdd4b5e705ab5","tid":203861,"uid":10071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:07:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警車有無關愛座</blockquote><br />\n法庭有無關愛座？"},{"pid":"81a52577573bb6e69131f1d1c4f8b5f864502db8","tid":203861,"uid":10071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>警車有無關愛座</blockquote><br />\n法庭有無關愛座？</blockquote><br />\n監倉有無關愛座？"},{"pid":"2ae206aef88f15f83576815e7dcf884cefe932d6","tid":203861,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"75歲廢老其實無野輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}